      <title>欧洲央行降息几乎已成定局：决策指南</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/ecb-interest-rate-cuts-another-move-all-but-certain-with-inflation-goal-in-view</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行将在第五次会议上降低利率，因为接近 2% 目标的通胀率让官员们进一步放松对经济的束缚。]]></description>
