    <item>
      <title>KKR 战略入股医疗供应商 Henry Schein</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/kkr-takes-strategic-stake-in-medical-supply-group-henry-schein</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR &amp; Co. 已收购 Henry Schein Inc. 12% 的股份，并将与该公司合作改善这家全球最大的向诊所牙医和医生销售医疗产品的分销商的运营。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/kkr-takes-strategic-stake-in-medical-supply-group-henry-schein</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 12:26:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士解除欧盟股市限制 关系改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/swiss-to-end-eu-stock-market-measures-amid-improving-relations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士将把欧盟从其股票市场保护名单中移除，从而结束 2019 年对瑞士股票在欧盟交易的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/swiss-to-end-eu-stock-market-measures-amid-improving-relations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 11:17:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
